Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.88,0:12:10.87,Style01,,0,0,0,,{\fs40.5\frz14.11\move(743.915,884,676.028,929,13,3975)}冈田化学研究所\N第2区 B栋\N第3区 D栋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.88,0:12:10.87,Style01,,0,0,0,,{\fs40.5\frz14.11\move(1048.873,113.75,981.521,157.25,13,3975)}。西屿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.88,0:12:10.87,Style01,,0,0,0,,{\fs40.5\frz14.11\move(1227.859,187.25,1150.254,235.25,13,3975)}弦神剑圣教会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.88,0:12:10.87,Style01,,0,0,0,,{\fs40.5\frz14.11\move(1240.873,257.75,1169.296,308.5,13,3975)}西欧中央教会
