Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.52,0:19:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,学长！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.02,0:19:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,共鸣？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.04,0:19:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这种能力是？
