Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.44,0:20:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,狮子王机关的可怜傀儡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.79,0:20:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,至少死于身为人类的我手下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.40,0:20:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,学...学长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.67,0:21:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,学长？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.93,0:21:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.27,0:21:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不要！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.40,0:21:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.29,0:21:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,亚丝塔露蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.99,0:21:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要夺回至宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.67,0:21:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,命令领受
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.67,0:21:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50}Accept
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.02,0:23:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这份罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.97,0:23:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我也一起承担吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.65,0:23:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我是学长的监视者啊！
